values:
i'm not too fond of everything that's happening to me right now, as i discussed with someone today. things get better, right?

all i want to do is lay my head on your shoulder akhdgfkajfhag

this year is pulling together rather nicely. most of the time.

ended up not going to danger and gave bob my ticket instead. for some reason i just didn't feel like driving into the city. definetly miss some people i could have seen there though.

i miss my best friends so much it makes my head spin.
(more than it normally does that is.)
but not in the "i wish how we use to be" way you'd assume.
if you know me then you know distance and i never take the same side.

listen to aaron gillespie's cover of wonderwall when your eyes just wont rest.

from now on entries will be public instead of friend locked. comments open & everything lurkable. 

wikiwikiword ;)

let me know what you really think about me or ask me a question and i'll be honest about the answer

it's all anonymous so say whatever you'd like, i dont have the skills to track who it is.
